nesday]]\n| caps3          = 0\n| goals3         = 0\n| years4         = 1892\u20131893\n| clubs4         = [[Grimsby Town F.C.|Grimsby Town]]\n| caps4          = 2\n| goals4         = 0\n| years5         = 1893\n| clubs5         = Chesterfield Rangers\n| caps5          = \n| goals5         = \n| totalcaps      = \n| totalgoals     = \n| nationalyears1 = 1887\n| nationalteam1  = [[England national football team|England]]\n| nationalcaps1  = 1\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n}}\n'''Edward Brayshaw''' (6 October 1863 \u2013 20 November 1908)<ref name=\"englandfootballonline\" /> was an English international [[association football|footballer]], who played as a [[Defender (association football)|centre half]].\n\n==Career==\nBorn in [[Sheffield]], Brayshaw played for [[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|The Wednesday]] and [[Grimsby Town F.C.|Grimsby Town]]<ref name=Joyce>{{cite book |last=Joyce |first=Michael |title=Football League Players' Records 1888 to 1939 |publisher=SoccerData |location=Nottingham |year=2004 |page=35 |isbn=978-1-899468-67-6}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Lamming|first1=Douglas|title=A who's who of Grimsby Town AFC : 1890-1985|date=1985|publisher=Hutton|location=Beverley|isbn=0-907033-34-2|page=18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.adrianbullock.com/swfc/stats/play0067.htm|title=Teddy Brayshaw|publisher=Sheffield Wednesday Archive |accessdate=2 July 2018 }}</ref> and earned one cap for [[England national football team|England]] in 1887.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Naylor |first1=Davey |title=Teddy Brayshaw |url=http://englandstats.com/players.php?pid=149 |website=englandstats |accessdate=2 July 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"englandfootballonline\">{{cite web |title=Teddy Brayshaw profile |url=http://www.englandfootballonline.com/TeamPlyrsBios/PlayersB/BioBrayshawE.html |website=englandfootballonline |accessdate=2 July 2018 |date=17 June 2015}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External Links==\n{{englandstats|id=149}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Brayshaw, Teddy}}\n[[Category:1863 births]]\n[[Category:1908 deaths]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:England international footballers]]\n[[Category:Walkley F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Sheffield Wednesday F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Grimsby Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Sheffield]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n{{England-footy-defender-1860s-stub}}\n", "name_user": "GiantSnowman", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teddy_Brayshaw"}
